OL,3,CHow this week's London Underground
OL,4,Cstrike affects you
OL,6,FTransport for London says buses, the
OL,7,FElizabeth line, DLR, London Overground
OL,8,Fand trams will be running as normal
OL,9,Fbut services are likely to be very
OL,10,Fbusy.
OL,12,FThe union is in dispute with London
OL,13,FUnderground over changes to the
OL,14,Fworking week, including shift patterns.
OL,16,FMore 24-hour strikes are planned in
OL,17,FJune unless the row is resolved.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
