OL,3,CHow this week's London Underground
OL,4,Cstrike affects you
OL,6,FPubs and restaurants fear losing trade
OL,7,Fthis week because of the industrial
OL,8,Faction as fewer workers than normal
OL,9,Fhave travelled to offices.
OL,11,FClaire Mann, TfL's Chief Operating
OL,12,FOfficer, said:"It isdisappointing
OL,13,Fthat the RMT is planning this strike
OL,14,Factiondespite our best efforts to
OL,15,Fresolve this dispute. We have been
OL,16,Fclear that our proposals for a four-
OL,17,Fday week are designed to improve work-
OL,18,Flife balance and are entirely
OL,19,Fvoluntary.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
