PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779199898
OL,3,CHow this week's London Underground
OL,4,Cstrike affects you
OL,6,F"Any Tube driver who doesn't wish to
OL,7,Fopt in to the new, four-day working
OL,8,Fpattern and associated changes to
OL,9,Fworking arrangements can remain on a
OL,10,Ffive-day working pattern. We have also
OL,11,Fsaid many times in discussions that we
OL,12,Fbelieve the majority of the issues
OL,13,Fthat have been raised would be
OL,14,Fresolved with more detailed work."
OL,16,FAn RMT spokesperson said: "Our members
OL,17,Ffeel that this is a 'fake four-day
OL,18,Fweek' that amounts to five days' work
OL,19,Fcompressed into four.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
