FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1779199898
OL,3,CHow this week's London Underground
OL,4,Cstrike affects you
OL,6,F"This includes reduced flexibility
OL,7,Fover shift patterns, with the
OL,8,Fpotential for only 24 hours notice of
OL,9,Fwhat shifts drivers will be doing,
OL,10,Fserious concerns from our members
OL,11,Fabout shift length and resulting
OL,12,Ffatigue impacting safety in a safety-
OL,13,Fcritical role like tube driving.
OL,15,F"Strikes remain on as we try to reach
OL,16,Fa negotiated settlement with TfL."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
